02:27.564 --> 02:29.107
<i>♪ Come and get your love</i>
<i>Come and get your love ♪</i>

02:29.191 --> 02:30.859
<i>♪ Come and get your love now ♪</i>

02:30.942 --> 02:31.985
[grunts] Ah!

02:32.069 --> 02:33.695
<i>♪ Come and get your love</i>
<i>Come and get your love ♪</i>

02:33.779 --> 02:35.572
<i>♪ Come and get your love now ♪</i>

